timeline.bodyText:
I think that you need to do Math.min after you computed corePoolSize again.
Like
{code}
if (corePoolSize <= 0) corePoolSize = Runtime.getRuntime().availableProcessors() * 2 : corePoolSize;
Math.min(corePoolSize, maxNumThreads);
{code}

